        <head>Lose Something</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Life's been here around </l>
          <l>without pressure </l>
          <l>When it comes to drop </l>
          <l>I do it better </l>
          <l>When I hear a song </l>
          <l>I want to rock </l>
          <l>It's better to rechoose </l>
          <l>Let's skip the talk </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>When I see a bird I wear my hat </l>
          <l>When it's getting dark I don't mind that </l>
          <l>When I see a field I think of dude </l>
          <l>When I lose something I think of you</l>
        </lg>
